snippet.title: STAR WARS™: The Old Republic™ Rise of the Hutt Cartel Launch Trailer
snippet.description: The first Digital Expansion: Rise of the Hutt Cartel has just launched, bringing with it an action-packed storyline focused on factional conflict against the Hutt Cartel. Watch the "Fight for Makeb" launch trailer to find out more about the new gear, new abilities and new challenges waiting for you in Rise of the Hutt Cartel and purchase a copy of the Digital Expansion now!
